text: Have you checked out the Gematro blog?
... As the Happening intensifies, are the Zaibatsus going to unpeel from Woke and re-attach their PR to right-wing apocalypse narratives?
... This is basically the Fall-Out narrative (which is intriguingly self-fulfilling). ...
... To misquote Fisher, if the only way to get to the end of the world is through the end of capitalism, that's cool.
Biden campaign is as if the Gods had booked the entire American ruling class onto the Titanic. It's a miraculous thing.
Is this kind of hysteria genuine, or merely performative?
Should be The Gnomic Metatrigon of the Eighth Gate, of course.
Your saintly patience with these idiots is extraordinary.
